1
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:12,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,150
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:11,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:12,020 --> 00:01:15,140
[Episode 28]

5
00:01:20,030 --> 00:01:20,780
Come here.

6
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,010
Your Highness!

7
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:32,780
Your spirit energy comes from Lifei.

8
00:01:34,030 --> 00:01:35,250
Only by drawing on her spirit energy

9
00:01:36,270 --> 00:01:37,290
can you help me.

10
00:01:44,550 --> 00:01:45,060
Simo!

11
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,650
Simo!

12
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,620
Simo!

13
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,290
Simo!

14
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:02,810
Simo!

15
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,170
Simo!

16
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:19,740
Everything will be fine.

17
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:22,180
Everything will be fine.

18
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,940
The demons expected our arrival,

19
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:54,370
so they left this.

20
00:02:58,550 --> 00:03:01,090
If we fail to hand over the Divine Tree by tomorrow's Chen hour,

21
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:05,060
two more heads will be sent to us.

22
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:06,530
Simo.

23
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,020
Have you found Simo?

24
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:13,780
Lifei,

25
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,090
don't go over there.

26
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:57,090
Lifei!

27
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:00,970
Lifei!

28
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:16,620
Simo,

29
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,500
the mushrooms in the woods taste so fresh.

30
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:23,790
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

31
00:04:23,790 --> 00:04:25,740
I even stole Elder Dongyang's chickens.

32
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,570
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

33
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:30,150
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

34
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:31,250
Tender and full of flavor.

35
00:04:31,590 --> 00:04:33,790
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

36
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:35,760
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

37
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,660
Simo,

38
00:04:38,030 --> 00:04:38,770
in the next life...

39
00:04:39,030 --> 00:04:41,390
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

40
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,510
♪No calamity can rival♪

41
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:45,420
Can I be your sister in the next life?

42
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,950
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43
00:04:49,090 --> 00:04:52,570
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44
00:04:53,330 --> 00:04:55,570
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

45
00:04:56,010 --> 00:04:59,050
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

46
00:04:59,690 --> 00:05:01,970
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

47
00:05:02,770 --> 00:05:06,250
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

48
00:05:06,810 --> 00:05:09,090
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

49
00:05:09,610 --> 00:05:11,560
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

50
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,210
Lifei, what's wrong?

51
00:05:13,290 --> 00:05:15,490
♪Reign supreme♪

52
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:19,120
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

53
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,620
I'm fine.

54
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:26,450
Since they're after me,

55
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,250
I'll put an end to all this.

56
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:56,890
Guardian,

57
00:05:57,230 --> 00:05:58,330
they wouldn't trade the Divine Tree

58
00:05:58,350 --> 00:05:59,770
for two ordinary disciples.

59
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,660
Jiang Lifei

60
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,570
will definitely come.

61
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,690
Guardian,

62
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,770
two disciples from the Wuyue Court are outside the valley.

63
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:13,980
The female disciple claims she is the Divine Tree.

64
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,940
Jiang Lifei,

65
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,210
you've finally come.

66
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:26,100
Where's Lei Xiuyuan?

67
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,180
He's waiting for you, of course.

68
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,010
After you.

69
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:33,060
Release Changyue and Ye Ye,

70
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,370
and I'll go with you.

71
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:51,940
Ye.

72
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:54,370
Are you alright?

73
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:31,770
It turns out

74
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,100
everything was destined long ago.

75
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,740
How do you fare?

76
00:07:40,910 --> 00:07:41,660
Can you hold on?

77
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,250
We're fine,

78
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:45,500
but they took Simo away.

79
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,370
Save him!

80
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,100
No need.

81
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,810
Simo

82
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,420
has returned to the Wuyue Court.

83
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,180
What about

84
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,500
Lifei then?

85
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,500
Don't worry,

86
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,450
we've got a plan.

87
00:07:59,080 --> 00:07:59,770
That's a relief.

88
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:02,450
We've scouted the valley.

89
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:04,500
A hundred demons remain inside.

90
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,810
Over fifty are in the southeast,

91
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,540
more than thirty are in the west,

92
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,180
and the fewest are in the east.

93
00:08:10,910 --> 00:08:11,500
Qiongqi

94
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,620
is in the southeast.

95
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,060
Where's Rakshasa?

96
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,100
She's in the cave with Xiuyuan.

97
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,740
I can't sense

98
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,010
his heartbeat anymore.

99
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,420
Take Ye Ye back to heal first.

100
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,370
We'll stand guard here

101
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,130
and wait for news from Lifei.

102
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,300
Alright.

103
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,970
He surely has a long life.

104
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,020
Even pierced by thousands of vines, he still lives.

105
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,260
You put him in this state.

106
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,330
Hurry and save him!

107
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,260
You killed Zhaomin,

108
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,610
Elder Guangwei,

109
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,970
and Simo,

110
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,690
yet you still expect me to save him.

111
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,610
Isn't that ridiculous?

112
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,260
Do you believe

113
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,690
I could kill you right now?

114
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,420
Your Demon Lord is on his last legs.

115
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:21,140
Killing or torturing me won't change a thing.

116
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,020
You brought me here

117
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:24,540
precisely to channel

118
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,970
my spirit to sustain his life, right?

119
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,090
Otherwise, he'll perish instantly.

120
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,330
Jiang Lifei,

121
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:36,180
you know well he never meant to harm you.

122
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:37,090
He'd sacrifice

123
00:09:37,230 --> 00:09:38,690
his own life for you.

124
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,060
What about you?

125
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,660
Have you no heart at all?

126
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:54,490
He has blood on his hands.

127
00:09:57,230 --> 00:09:59,060
What about all the lives he took?

128
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,020
A murderer is a murderer,

129
00:10:02,710 --> 00:10:03,540
no excuses.

130
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,690
Jiang Lifei,

131
00:10:05,630 --> 00:10:07,660
even if he wronged the whole world,

132
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,300
he never wronged you.

133
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:11,900
Because of you,

134
00:10:12,160 --> 00:10:13,380
he has ended up like this.

135
00:10:13,470 --> 00:10:14,450
You doubted him,

136
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,940
and you killed him yourself.

137
00:10:22,280 --> 00:10:23,260
I never doubted him.

138
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,690
But I can't let more people die for this.

139
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:37,660
What are you doing?

140
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:41,330
Let go.

141
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,610
I'll save him.

142
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:55,780
How...

143
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,020
How will you save him?

144
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,940
With my own blood.

145
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:54,730
Xiuyuan,

146
00:11:55,710 --> 00:11:56,570
this must end.

147
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,180
Activate the Four Symbols Divine Fire Formation with the Zhurong Stone

148
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:13,780
and channel the Divine Tree's power

149
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,060
to trap the demons

150
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,690
and strip them of all strength.

151
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,420
We'll charge in

152
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:19,810
and wipe them all out at once.

153
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,140
Lifei,

154
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:34,730
why are you here?

155
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,420
What's going on?

156
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:00,490
Did Ji Tongzhou tell you to do this?

157
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:03,420
Why?

158
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,020
For Zhaomin

159
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:08,660
and Simo.

160
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,380
This is our destined fate.

161
00:13:29,040 --> 00:13:29,780
We've been trapped!

162
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,540
The Divine Tree came to slay us.

163
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:20,020
Stop!

164
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,180
Stop!

165
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:44,300
Lifei,

166
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:46,140
you may take my life.

167
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:48,180
Spare us from mutual slaughter.

168
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,180
Grant me just a little more time,

169
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,060
please.

170
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:57,920
♪The warmth within my arms♪

171
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,380
Grant you time?

172
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:01,320
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

173
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,020
So you can kill more people?

174
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:04,590
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

175
00:15:04,590 --> 00:15:05,060
No.

176
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,450
I will send them back to their homeland.

177
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:09,420
Trust me.

178
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:12,240
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

179
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:15,760
♪I can no longer tell you♪

180
00:15:16,160 --> 00:15:19,360
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

181
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:22,680
♪Utter that line♪

182
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,760
♪Knowing love and hate♪

183
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:29,000
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

184
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,960
♪I still linger on♪

185
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:36,560
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

186
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:41,320
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

187
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:44,560
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

188
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:45,610
Rakshasa.

189
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:48,320
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

190
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:49,780
Rakshasa.

191
00:15:49,780 --> 00:15:51,800
♪I wish you well♪

192
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,800
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

193
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:58,080
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

194
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,160
♪You're still screaming♪

195
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:00,900
Rakshasa!

196
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:05,110
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

197
00:16:05,110 --> 00:16:05,730
Lifei,

198
00:16:07,110 --> 00:16:08,140
be careful not to hurt yourself.

199
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:10,360
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

200
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:12,200
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

201
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,850
Why won't any of you believe me?

202
00:16:13,850 --> 00:16:16,920
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

203
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:18,260
Why?

204
00:16:20,570 --> 00:16:24,760
♪Just to keep you safe♪

205
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:41,450
My Lord.

206
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:51,210
Darn that Divine Tree.

207
00:16:52,470 --> 00:16:53,020
Watch out!

208
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:55,660
Tongzhou!

209
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,420
Everyone, follow me.

210
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:21,290
Don't worry.

211
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,860
Ye Ye's mostly healed from his wounds.

212
00:17:24,510 --> 00:17:25,820
Tongzhou will recover, too.

213
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:28,900
All demons in Lilie Valley fled

214
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:30,580
with the Demon Lord.

215
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,450
They won't come after you again.

216
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,380
It's all my fault.

217
00:17:36,710 --> 00:17:38,050
I truly am an ill omen.

218
00:17:39,880 --> 00:17:40,490
Lifei,

219
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,100
don't blame yourself.

220
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:43,900
I'm fine.

221
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:45,050
Stay still.

222
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:46,290
I'll heal you.

223
00:17:57,750 --> 00:17:58,490
Be careful.

224
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:02,860
You're severely hurt.

225
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:04,690
You should rest for a few more days.

226
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,940
If I rest any longer,

227
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,970
I'll become useless.

228
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:27,340
Here.

229
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,340
Lifei,

230
00:18:38,710 --> 00:18:39,970
do you still hate Xiuyuan?

231
00:18:50,470 --> 00:18:51,580
Between us,

232
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:55,340
there is not even hatred left.

233
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:56,530
Lifei,

234
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,250
Xiuyuan didn't kill Simo.

235
00:19:00,230 --> 00:19:01,490
You met when you were young,

236
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:03,530
endured countless hardships side by side,

237
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,100
and loved each other deeply.

238
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:07,010
Why not give him another chance?

239
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,180
Look,

240
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,290
the Fragrance Bond has vanished.

241
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:31,100
From now on,

242
00:19:32,120 --> 00:19:33,530
there is no bond between us.

243
00:19:34,470 --> 00:19:35,340
I stand apart

244
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:37,450
from him.

245
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,050
There is no chance

246
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:00,250
left for us.

247
00:20:02,990 --> 00:20:03,970
But the Divine Lord...

248
00:20:04,360 --> 00:20:05,050
Be careful.

249
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:07,420
Xiuyuan's

250
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:11,140
whole life has been fraught with misfortune.

251
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,420
His greatest wish in this lifetime

252
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:16,180
was to become an ordinary person

253
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:17,690
and spend his days with you.

254
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,970
May heaven show mercy to him,

255
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,140
leaving him a way forward.

256
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:27,180
Gelin and Lu Li sent word days ago

257
00:20:28,030 --> 00:20:30,420
that signs of the Sea Calamity have appeared in the East Sea.

258
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:35,490
We'll eventually face a life-or-death battle.

259
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:37,900
No one knows

260
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:40,210
how many will survive after that.

261
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:22,010
Master,

262
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:23,290
at the hour of Mao today,

263
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:24,900
the sea level of the East Sea dropped by eight inches.

264
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,420
Five thousand li eastward across the waters,

265
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,290
thunderclouds roiled endlessly.

266
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:28,620
I can't tell what causes it.

267
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:34,010
The heavenly thunder disaster is coming.

268
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:37,620
The five-hundred-year Sea Calamity

269
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:39,970
is upon us.

270
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:03,210
My Lord.

271
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,290
The Guardian has settled down.

272
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:05,420
She is out of danger for now.

273
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:06,340
I see.

274
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,490
My Lord,

275
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:12,210
our clansmen have rushed here.

276
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,900
Five centuries have passed.

277
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:23,940
It's time they came.

278
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:45,820
Tongzhou!

279
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:47,820
What happened?

280
00:22:58,640 --> 00:22:59,290
Lifei,

281
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:00,820
I'm fine.

282
00:23:02,270 --> 00:23:03,530
Don't waste your spirit energy on me.

283
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:05,730
Silence. Calm your breath to recover.

284
00:23:15,440 --> 00:23:16,100
Your Highness!

285
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:19,940
Your Highness!

286
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:24,970
What exactly is wrong with him?

287
00:23:25,470 --> 00:23:26,450
He hasn't fully healed,

288
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,100
yet he forced himself to cultivate the Sacred Fire.

289
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,380
I'll ease his spirit aura later.

290
00:23:30,710 --> 00:23:31,340
He should be alright.

291
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:33,490
How could he possibly be alright?

292
00:23:35,230 --> 00:23:36,010
Lifei,

293
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,450
he pushed himself to cultivate it for you.

294
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,100
For me?

295
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:46,210
His Highness was secluded in Duantu to break through,

296
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:48,690
yet he rushed to the Wuyue Court

297
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,250
to rescue you,

298
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,100
leaving internal injuries back then.

299
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,660
Then he fought battle after battle

300
00:23:53,790 --> 00:23:54,970
with no time to catch his breath.

301
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:56,730
These days,

302
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,380
crowds keep coming to confront him

303
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,820
over the Divine Tree matter.

304
00:24:00,510 --> 00:24:02,250
He had to coax and deter them

305
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:03,340
to send them away.

306
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:05,100
He's worn himself ragged

307
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,490
and now gravely wounded once more.

308
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:09,010
He tried to accelerate his cultivation

309
00:24:09,310 --> 00:24:10,860
to recover early,

310
00:24:11,470 --> 00:24:11,940
so

311
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:14,010
he could protect you.

312
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,210
You're...

313
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,100
You're Miaoqing?

314
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,530
Why are you dressed like this?

315
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:27,490
His Highness reshaped my body

316
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:30,420
and mended my soul.

317
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:32,290
I wish

318
00:24:33,470 --> 00:24:35,660
to stay by his side as a disciple

319
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:36,860
of the Xingzheng Hall.

320
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,970
My face bears scars,

321
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,620
so I wear a veil.

322
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,010
I'm sorry.

323
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,580
You endured such terrible wounds for me,

324
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:50,290
yet I failed to recognize you.

325
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:51,450
Lifei,

326
00:24:52,470 --> 00:24:53,620
your sect suffered a catastrophe,

327
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,010
and you had enough troubles.

328
00:24:55,710 --> 00:24:57,180
Naturally, you didn't recognize me.

329
00:24:58,230 --> 00:24:59,620
But I hope

330
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:04,380
you understand how much His Highness endures.

331
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,820
He has no one left

332
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,580
but you now.

333
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:12,730
Please stand by him.

334
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:16,490
Don't worry.

335
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:19,940
Tongzhou will pull through.

336
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,690
I'll find a way to save him.

337
00:25:58,070 --> 00:25:58,730
What's wrong?

338
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:00,380
Healed Tongzhou again?

339
00:26:01,470 --> 00:26:03,490
Even if the Divine Tree's spirit energy is boundless,

340
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:05,100
don't exhaust it this way.

341
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,580
Your body won't bear it.

342
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:07,900
I'm fine.

343
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,100
I'm tough,

344
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:11,420
and just a short rest will do.

345
00:26:11,470 --> 00:26:12,010
You...

346
00:26:14,990 --> 00:26:16,010
Are your injuries healed?

347
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,250
Look,

348
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:20,620
much better now.

349
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:22,420
Lifei,

350
00:26:23,230 --> 00:26:24,380
Changyue and I

351
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:26,100
came to bid you farewell.

352
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,100
Are you heading back to the Dizang Sect?

353
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,380
There's no need to return

354
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,010
to that shameful sect.

355
00:26:35,070 --> 00:26:35,730
The East Sea is in peril.

356
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,290
Gelin has rushed back to the Wanxian Sect.

357
00:26:37,710 --> 00:26:39,820
We plan to head for the East Sea, too.

358
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:41,730
Before that,

359
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,620
we'll visit a place.

360
00:26:44,470 --> 00:26:45,580
Before Simo died,

361
00:26:46,030 --> 00:26:46,900
he asked us

362
00:26:48,510 --> 00:26:50,100
to visit his parents and family

363
00:26:50,510 --> 00:26:51,340
on his behalf.

364
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:56,100
We're going to his hometown.

365
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:04,380
When you see his parents,

366
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:05,490
please give this to them for me.

367
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:11,770
Alright.

368
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,140
We'll meet in Duanming City.

369
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,490
Patrol thoroughly.

370
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:35,860
Yes.

371
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:09,770
My Lord, thank you for using your energy to heal me.

372
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:12,620
I deserve death for my mistakes.

373
00:28:13,470 --> 00:28:14,690
I even turned against you before.

374
00:28:14,710 --> 00:28:16,180
Let bygones be bygones.

375
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:20,770
We're outside the mountain-sea barrier now.

376
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:23,210
They won't chase us for the time being.

377
00:28:27,510 --> 00:28:28,940
The strange ocean currents lately

378
00:28:29,510 --> 00:28:31,180
are clear signs of the Sea Calamity.

379
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:34,180
Our clansmen know you've returned

380
00:28:34,470 --> 00:28:35,940
and are hurrying here.

381
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:38,380
What's your plan, My Lord?

382
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:49,770
Once the Sea Calamity strikes,

383
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:53,050
heavenly thunder and earth fire will shatter the mountain-sea barrier

384
00:28:53,400 --> 00:28:54,820
and engulf Duanming City.

385
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,690
We can take this chance

386
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:58,660
to avenge the siege of the Lilie Valley

387
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:02,340
and avenge five centuries of shame upon our clan.

388
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:07,420
The Sea Calamity shall consume the world

389
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:08,940
and raze all the Central Plains.

390
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,250
Do you think the demon clan will survive?

391
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:13,210
At worst, we'll perish together.

392
00:29:14,030 --> 00:29:15,100
We crossed the sea,

393
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:16,580
seeking a homeland,

394
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,900
not a burial ground in a foreign land.

395
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,860
Then what is your plan, My Lord?

396
00:29:25,310 --> 00:29:26,380
Stop this at once!

397
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:29,530
Speak calmly.

398
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:42,210
My Lord.

399
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,940
Your return has lifted all our spirits.

400
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,210
We should strike now,

401
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:52,660
shatter the mountain-sea barrier,

402
00:29:52,990 --> 00:29:54,210
and catch them completely off guard.

403
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:57,420
The battle at the Lilie Valley

404
00:29:57,990 --> 00:29:59,250
left our clan gravely weakened.

405
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:02,050
Do you believe we can emerge unharmed

406
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,180
if we wage another war now?

407
00:30:09,160 --> 00:30:10,140
The heavenly tribulation descends.

408
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,690
If I witness you fighting each other again,

409
00:30:14,270 --> 00:30:16,940
I shall show no mercy.

410
00:30:18,750 --> 00:30:19,660
Understood.

411
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,180
My Lord.

412
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:48,620
My Lord,

413
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:50,620
you look far more haggard

414
00:30:51,550 --> 00:30:53,140
than you did five centuries ago.

415
00:30:57,230 --> 00:30:58,290
Have you met me before?

416
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:01,580
I had the honor of seeing you once

417
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,730
back in our homeland overseas.

418
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,770
In that lifetime,

419
00:31:05,990 --> 00:31:06,660
you promised

420
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:08,490
you would lead our clansmen

421
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,940
to find a blessed land to dwell in.

422
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:15,660
A blessed land?

423
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,900
Obviously, I've led you into an abyss.

424
00:31:20,510 --> 00:31:22,180
This is not your fault.

425
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:24,970
Our clan is nurtured by the world's spirit nourishment.

426
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:26,450
When the spiritual energy runs thin,

427
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:28,100
sickness plagues us.

428
00:31:28,710 --> 00:31:31,210
The lands overseas have run dry of spirit energy.

429
00:31:31,510 --> 00:31:33,820
Countless clansmen have strange illnesses

430
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,250
and can't survive.

431
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,450
That is why

432
00:31:37,470 --> 00:31:40,140
we chose to follow you willingly.

433
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,180
Yet we never imagined

434
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,180
the Central Plains would not

435
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,900
be a blessed land, either.

436
00:31:47,230 --> 00:31:48,450
I often think

437
00:31:48,790 --> 00:31:50,690
of our homeland.

438
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:54,450
If I could return there before I die,

439
00:31:55,070 --> 00:31:57,140
I would die without regret.

440
00:31:58,120 --> 00:32:00,250
Perhaps our clan's decline

441
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,380
is our destined fate.

442
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:05,380
Destined fate?

443
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,140
My Lord.

444
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:11,530
Even if the destined fate

445
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,450
can be turned around.

446
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:23,050
Listen to me,

447
00:32:23,470 --> 00:32:24,730
don't push yourself hard in cultivation.

448
00:32:27,550 --> 00:32:28,140
And

449
00:32:28,710 --> 00:32:29,860
I don't need your protection.

450
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:32,010
If anyone troubles you,

451
00:32:32,030 --> 00:32:32,860
send them straight to me.

452
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:35,140
But...

453
00:32:35,230 --> 00:32:36,050
Have a good rest.

454
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:38,290
Lifei.

455
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:39,210
Lifei.

456
00:32:46,710 --> 00:32:47,210
Bring this

457
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,380
with you.

458
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:51,770
Those coveting the Divine Tree

459
00:32:52,360 --> 00:32:53,420
will never give up.

460
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:55,010
Wear it, and it'll make them

461
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,940
think twice before striking.

462
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:58,970
From this day forward,

463
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:00,290
you are the most important person

464
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:02,820
to me, the Yue State and the Xingzheng Hall.

465
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:07,250
Lifei,

466
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:08,730
promise me.

467
00:33:09,270 --> 00:33:10,530
I will devote all I have

468
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:13,940
to protect you forever.

469
00:33:18,360 --> 00:33:19,580
I know you mean well.

470
00:33:21,230 --> 00:33:21,860
Tongzhou,

471
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:24,050
you will always be my closest friend.

472
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:26,820
I have my own path to walk.

473
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:29,210
I can't live under your protection forever.

474
00:33:30,070 --> 00:33:31,450
Are you still thinking of Lei Xiuyuan?

475
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,580
He's the Demon Lord.

476
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:35,660
It has nothing to do with him.

477
00:33:40,550 --> 00:33:41,690
Drink your medicine and rest early.

478
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,340
Your Highness.

479
00:34:14,550 --> 00:34:15,490
Calm your anger.

480
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:19,450
Lifei has just endured great difficulties

481
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,170
with no mind for romantic affections.

482
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:22,700
In time,

483
00:34:23,070 --> 00:34:25,300
she will understand your sincere heart.

484
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:28,860
She understands everything,

485
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,700
but she refuses to accept me.

486
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:36,700
Then

487
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:40,090
will you let go?

488
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,010
No.

489
00:34:49,720 --> 00:34:50,780
If that's the case,

490
00:34:52,190 --> 00:34:54,300
your genuine devotion

491
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,860
will eventually win her heart.

492
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:32,300
Her Divine Tree spirit energy works wonders indeed.

493
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,010
Miaoqing,

494
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:05,010
would you be my Lifei?

495
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:08,940
I shall obey

496
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:11,260
whatever you command.

497
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:21,300
It's a pity

498
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:24,820
that you're not her.

499
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:54,050
The Sea Calamity draws near.

500
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,130
Lifei will head to Duanming City.

501
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,220
I must stop hiding in the academy.

502
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:04,650
Master, please let me go.

503
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,380
Very well.

504
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:20,010
When the nest falls, no egg stays intact.

505
00:37:20,510 --> 00:37:21,490
We cultivate immortality

506
00:37:21,990 --> 00:37:23,380
precisely for such moments.

507
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:26,300
If we can avert this calamity,

508
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,700
it shall be a blessing for all living beings.

509
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:33,130
Cuixuan damaged your spirit meridians.

510
00:37:33,550 --> 00:37:34,260
If you go,

511
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:37,260
never recklessly wield your spirit energy.

512
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:40,010
Otherwise, it'll cost you your life.

513
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:41,420
I shall remember.

514
00:37:43,550 --> 00:37:44,170
Please

515
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:47,050
look after Mu.

516
00:37:48,070 --> 00:37:49,420
Rest assured.

517
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:52,700
She is part of our academy.

518
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:55,130
The academy will keep her safe.

519
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:34,970
Mu,

520
00:38:37,590 --> 00:38:38,740
I'm leaving soon.

521
00:38:40,990 --> 00:38:41,940
But

522
00:38:43,470 --> 00:38:45,490
I have no idea when I'll be back.

523
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:47,740
There's something I've hidden

524
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,970
from you all this time.

525
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:53,260
Mu,

526
00:38:55,470 --> 00:38:56,700
actually, I'm Yecha,

527
00:38:58,720 --> 00:39:00,090
another Guardian of the demon clan.

528
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:08,010
During the war against the immortals five centuries ago,

529
00:39:09,470 --> 00:39:10,530
I was cast into the bottom of the sea.

530
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:13,130
When I woke,

531
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:15,940
I'd transformed into a boy

532
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,530
of eleven or twelve.

533
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,380
I refused to give up

534
00:39:37,110 --> 00:39:38,340
and wanted to take revenge on Qingcheng.

535
00:39:39,190 --> 00:39:40,650
I tracked him down by every means

536
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:43,570
and followed him in secret.

537
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:45,740
Yet I found him

538
00:39:45,760 --> 00:39:47,940
gathering the bones of my fallen clansmen

539
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,380
and building the Outcast Tomb.

540
00:40:06,030 --> 00:40:07,570
I thought it was hypocrisy

541
00:40:08,470 --> 00:40:09,570
and resolved to slay him.

542
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:12,260
So I snuck up to strike him

543
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:13,860
from behind,

544
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:19,130
but he sensed my attack.

545
00:40:23,720 --> 00:40:27,300
All my memories were gone when I regained consciousness.

546
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:30,940
As I had no one to rely on,

547
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:33,170
Qingcheng set aside our enmity

548
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:35,090
and took me as his disciple.

549
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:57,380
As time passed, my memories slowly returned.

550
00:40:58,630 --> 00:41:01,740
But I grew as close to him as father and son

551
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:04,820
and could not bring myself to harm him.

552
00:41:06,240 --> 00:41:06,940
Later,

553
00:41:07,990 --> 00:41:09,820
as I had grown up,

554
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,010
he sent me to the Chufeng Academy

555
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,740
to let me learn

556
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:16,650
what a true immortal sect is like.

557
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,530
After that,

558
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,420
I went to the Wuyue Court

559
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,820
and became a disciple of Master Guangwei.

560
00:41:23,630 --> 00:41:24,490
That was when I met you.

561
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,780
Master Qingcheng

562
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,420
always knew my nature.

563
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:32,650
He firmly believed

564
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:35,170
immortals and demons would reconcile.

565
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:40,130
He spent his whole life striving for that,

566
00:41:40,550 --> 00:41:42,740
gathering countless ancient scrolls and treasures.

567
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,260
I'll bring all of them

568
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:46,090
with me to the East Sea.

569
00:41:47,670 --> 00:41:50,090
I hope I can fulfill his lifelong aspiration

570
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:53,570
and find a chance for reconciliation.

571
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:57,900
Let's check over there.

572
00:41:58,150 --> 00:41:58,860
Yes.

573
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:14,010
With the Xuantian power, open the Biluo Path.

574
00:42:14,510 --> 00:42:17,610
Follow this compass, and you may return to the land overseas.

575
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,220
To lead my clansmen back home,

576
00:42:25,590 --> 00:42:28,970
I must find the Xuantian Biluo Plate.

577
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,170
It's the curse.

578
